{ Annotated by GM Axel Bachmann - https://lichess.org/@/ABachmann

In a very unusual turn of events (half joking, half serious), Sindarov has finally conceded a draw versus Giri in Round 7 of the Candidates. The brilliant Uzbek player pushed as hard as he could, but Anish showed great resistance, to save a very important 0.5 points that keep his chances alive. }
