A great fight between two great players. Sindarov pressed as hard as he could, but Giri showed his class by defending a very challenging position.
With this game finished, the first half of the Candidates is officially over. The current standings show Sindarov in the clear lead, with an 1.5 points advantage over the closest rival, Fabiano Caruana (and a huge 2.5 difference over Giri and Pragg). But with 7 rounds to go, there are plenty of emotions left! } { [%clk 0:22:40] } 1/2-1/2


